=Description=

"Consensys is a “venture production studio” in the decentralization space. ConsenSys is pioneering a new approach to software development, deployment, utilization and revenue generation.

ConsenSys is a “hub” organization that identifies opportunities for software component development, cross-venture sharing of components, and promoting cross-fertilization of ideas.

ConsenSys is building blockchain-resident tools to enable all of its projects to be organized, governed, funded and executed on the blockchain. Due to the fluid nature of development and deployment in this new paradigm, all ConsenSys projects are considered “spokes” in different stages, from ideation, to emergence as proofs of concept, to productization, and ideally to eventually attain a dynamic balance of independent governance and interdependent relationships with related projects."

